item.title: IMG_4714 Welcome to the Jungle
item.description:
Alan G. Archer posted a photo:

This is a mirrored construct based on Dorothea Lange's first documentary photograph, White Angel Bread Line, San Francisco (1933 negative; ca. 1945 gelatin silver print).

Portland Art Museum, Portland, Oregon

Camera: Canon EOS 6D
Lens: Canon EF 35mm f/2
Exposure: 1/80 sec. @ f/4, ISO 1250

Media:
* San Francisco Story: "The Legend of Lois Jordan’s White Angel Jungle," by Woody LaBounty, June 12, 2024
* Wikipedia: Dorothea Lange
